---
---
<section class="bg-ink py-28 relative overflow-hidden" aria-label="Chamada final">
  <!-- Decorative circles -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/8 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-80 h-80 bg-accent/6 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <div class="gsap-reveal">
      <img
        src="/imgs/365-branding-digital-pages.avif"
        alt="Páginas do livro 365 Dias de Branding"
        width="340" height="240"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mx-auto mb-10 rounded-2xl max-w-xs"
      />

      <!-- Stars -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
        <span class="stars text-2xl">★★★★★</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-5 leading-tight">
        1 exercício para cada dia do ano<br class="hidden sm:block" /> na sua marca.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10 text-white/70 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Comece hoje a construir a marca que você sempre sonhou. O 365 Dias de Branding é o seu melhor amigo de execução.
      </p>

      <a
        href="#pricing"
        class="btn-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-accent text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-5 rounded-full shadow-2xl shadow-accent/30 hover:bg-accent-dark transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer"
      >
        Sim, quero o Guia Prático 365DB!
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>

      <p class="text-sm mt-6 text-white/50">
        Versão digital a partir de <strong class="text-white/80">3x R$87,31</strong> · Acesso imediato
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
